{
  "stem": "4187.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then I thought sometimes to myself, my goodness, that is someone's daughter, someone's mother, someone's grandmother, someone-- it's a person.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's a person.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That hair belonged to a person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that wasn't so bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What stuck us-- struck us was they didn't have any hair-- completely shaven off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the eyes were a sort of-- [MAKES EYES BIG] as if they didn't know where they were, just, you now, the vague looking around of people who really don't know who they are, or where they are, or what--",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we decided that these must be insane.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So this obviously is an area where the insane is being kept, because quite obviously, they-- they obviously are mad.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] because all these things-- in-- in-- in-- through the wires, so you couldn't truly tell what you saw.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You just had impressions of things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But by then-- of course, the train was very slow-- because we were inside.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we got in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The train stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as I remember, the ramp, rather like a-- a U, but not rounded U, but that way, that way, that way.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we came in on this side.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the doors eventually opened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we immediately, of course, which was what we had right through everywhere-- schnell, schnell, schnell, schnell, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Quickly, out, out, out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Jews, get out, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And if people weren't quick enough, then, of course, the whips came out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So people were literally whipped off the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember one woman, who were-- who was quite obviously petrified, and-- and got, sort of, psychologically stuck inside of the opening of the-- the cattle truck.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was whipped, and she fell out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, again, she screamed first.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, she fell out.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
